./migration-artifacts/09-governance/decision-log.md:63:- Decision: Task-local artifacts are generated under migration-artifacts/art-126_decision_log, while the contract-visible governance markdown is mirrored to migration-artifacts/09-governance/decision-log.md.
./migration-artifacts/09-governance/decision-log.md:64:- Rationale: The execution packet requires art-126 task artifacts, and the contract manifest requires the governance decision log at migration-artifacts/09-governance/decision-log.md with ART-126_DECISION_LOG as producer.
./migration-artifacts/09-governance/decision-log.md:70:### ADR-ART126-005 - Use proof records and heartbeat files as execution completion evidence
./migration-artifacts/09-governance/decision-log.md:75:- Decision: A task is complete only when generated artifacts exist, registry registration reports matching hashes, validation evidence is linked, heartbeat state is updated, and proof_records contains the task proof.
./migration-artifacts/09-governance/decision-log.md:76:- Rationale: The packet completion gate requires artifact existence, recorded hash, and linked validation evidence; the existing execution framework stores proofs and heartbeats per task.
./migration-artifacts/09-governance/decision-log.md:87:- Decision: Decision-log generation writes only migration-artifacts, execution-framework logs, state, scripts, and proof records allowed by the task packet.
./migration-artifacts/09-governance/decision-log.md:88:- Rationale: The packet scope permits migration-artifacts and execution-framework paths while blocking environment files, secrets, private keys, PEM files, and key files.
./migration-artifacts/09-governance/decision-log.md:89:- Evidence: `execution-framework/generated/execution_packets/ART-126_DECISION_LOG.json`, `execution-framework/scripts/artifact_registry.py`
./migration-artifacts/09-governance/decision-log.md:99:- Decision: Artifact proof is generated by applying the package migrations to an in-memory SQLite database, inserting a task run and operation, and registering the generated files through the same ArtifactRegistry path used by REQ-024.
./migration-artifacts/09-governance/decision-log.md:101:- Evidence: `execution-framework/generated/envctl_migration_db_model.json`, `execution-framework/scripts/verify_envctl_db_schema.py`, `execution-framework/scripts/artifact_registry.py`
